data.description: SHORT SALE. BEAUTIFULLY MAINTAINED HOME inside and out. This 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home features 2,337 square feet of living area with 2,964 total square feet under roof. Interior features include huge 21x12 living room and 20x15 family room. Eat in kitc,hen overlooks family room. Master bedroom is downstairs and features dual sinks, garden bath, separate shower and walk in closet. Upstairs includes 2 bedrooms, loft and full bath. This home is conveniently located approximately 1 mile from HWY 417. Just minutes to the coastal beach, attractions and 30 minutes to Orlando's famous area theme parks. This home is located in a private gated community. NO REAR NEIGHBORS!! Home backs up to conservation area!! Enjoy relaxing with a view in the huge 29x13 screen enclosed and covered backyard patio. Pride in ownership is evident thoughout this amazing home. PRICED TO SELL!!!Brokered And Advertised By: PREFERRED REAL ESTATEListing Agent: RONALD CLARK
